{"tid":665262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"極恐怖，唔知咩人嚟！","createTime":"2018-05-14T19:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T17:41:25.000Z","uid":74177,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"971fb7bd46e0b1ff2054d2939ff8e642206dc6f2","tid":665262,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:19:24.000Z","msg":"有無住公屋嘅巴打發現每逢凌晨一點左右<br />\n大門口就會有D怪聲，沙沙聲咁<br />\n我啱大概凌晨一點聽到有怪聲，我就喺個防盜眼望出去<br />\n發現有個男人拎住D紙攝喺每一家門口鐵閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時我都無打開門睇佢攝咗D咩紙喺度<br />\n但到啱啱三點，又有另一個男人行過收走每一家鐵閘攝住個張白色紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底喺咩人嚟？喺咪爆格黨嘅新手法？<br />\n好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018f19b14518f6f98523f2fba265f94f5e44ce14","tid":665262,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:20:16.000Z","msg":"有無巴打答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270d0ef391caef0de95b22930f8e1c045882e28c","tid":665262,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:22:55.000Z","msg":"聽到其他屋都有好多人慢慢開鐵閘嘅聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3989409f1bdfd038d4a77f69384ca52bb9a65f9","tid":665262,"uid":128658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:22:55.000Z","msg":"建議報定警<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefe123d52f6a37beac233d30a0c2f2030241db8","tid":665262,"uid":90310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T19:23:01.000Z","msg":"派傳單姐"},{"pid":"2e2cbb2b1c950271a1aaf7817d2f9847f21a1872","tid":665262,"uid":74177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aefe123d52f6a37beac233d30a0c2f2030241db8","tid":665262,"